,{"kind":"text","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fs~AT","text_ar":"فسّاط"},{"kind":"text","text":", because it is more regular to change the latter of two identical letters than to change the former, and because the two identical letters in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fs~AT","text_ar":"فسّاط"},{"kind":"text","text":"are together, whereas the two identical letters in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fsTAT","text_ar":"فسطاط"},{"kind":"text","text":"are separated, (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusotaAtN","text_ar":"فُسْتَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fisotaAtN","text_ar":"فِسْتَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) altogether eight different forms, but MF observes that Esh-Shiháb El-Kastalánee gives twelve, [which, however, he does not transcribe, the remaining four being probably with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"f","text_ar":"ف"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tent of hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"-cloth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great tent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of structure"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Z)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used in travelling, less than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suraAdiq","text_ar":"سُرَادِق"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Z:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of structure called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suraAdiq","text_ar":"سُرَادِق"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaATiyTu","text_ar":"فَسَاطِيطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, Msb, TA;) for which they did not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaAtiyTu","text_ar":"فَسَاتِيطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, TA:) ―         -b2-  Hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusoTaATN","text_ar":"فُسْطَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A city:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any city:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a city in which is the general place of assemblage of people:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a populous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comprehensive, city;"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to some: (Msb:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of assemblage of the people of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuwrap","text_ar":"كُورَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which means a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"city,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"district,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"region"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Lth, Az, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"around their general mosque:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) or you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusoTaATu AlmiSori","text_ar":"فُسْطَاطُ المِصْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place of assemblage of the people of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mSr","text_ar":"مصر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"city"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"around their congregational mosque."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusoTaATu","text_ar":"فُسْطَاطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so in two copies of the S] is [a name of] The city of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miSor","text_ar":"مِصْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the metropolis of Egypt]: (S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfusoTaATu","text_ar":"الفُسْطَاطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also the proper name of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miSoruAlEatiyqapu","text_ar":"مِصْرُالعَتِيقَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) the city so called, (TA,) which was built by 'Amr Ibn-El- 'Ás; (K, TA;) the city of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mSr","text_ar":"مصر"},{"kind":"text","text":"in old times; as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfisoTaATu","text_ar":"الفِسْطَاطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaSorapu","text_ar":"البَصْرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","TA","Mgh","Z","Lth","Az"]}]}}